doc.after: At the time of rebranding the Britannia Airways fleet consisted of the following aircraft  From the 1980s onwards Britannia operated a solely Boeing fleet unlike their rivals which flew Boeing aircraft alongside Airbus and McDonnell Douglas aircraft Britannia however did at times lease Airbus aircraft
